---
description: Protect reference-only folders from edits
alwaysApply: true
---

The CODE_PROJECTS folder is informational reference material only.

Rules:
- never modify files inside CODE_PROJECTS
- never refactor files inside CODE_PROJECTS
- never move or rename files inside CODE_PROJECTS
- never include CODE_PROJECTS files in commits for KeyPilot changes
- use CODE_PROJECTS only for inspiration or reference

All active development must occur outside CODE_PROJECTS.
